+## 0. SSOT One-Liner
+
+`ASH-BASETRAIN-GPU-39`는 38에서 PASS된 selected row-block bounded MatVec candidate를 확장해, **GPU upload slot을 명시적으로 임대(Lease) → 적재(Fill) → 업로드(Upload) → 커널 사용(DispatchUse) → readback 검증(ReadbackVerified) → 반납(Release)하는 Atlas Upload Ring Buffer 상태기계를 봉인하는 패치**다.
+
+```txt
+38 PASS bounded MatVec candidate
+↓
+Atlas upload ring buffer create
+↓
+slot lease
+↓
+selected row-block payload fill
+↓
+GPU upload
+↓
+bounded MatVec candidate uses leased slot
+↓
+output readback + parity
+↓
+slot release
+↓
+39 runtime receipt write
+```
+
